</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-45_ pf-text-1"><strong>The Management of Health and Safety at Work Regulations 1999</strong> - mandates employers to assess and mitigate risks to their employees' health and safety, including providing first aid equipment, facilities, and trained personnel.


